<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-register">How to Register</h3>
<ol>
<li>To register a SportyBet account please visit www.SportyBet.com and click on the “Register” button on the top-right of the Home page, or try our Instant Registration.</li>
<li>Fill in the form with your phone number and password to create an account, or log in via Facebook.</li>
<li>You will receive a verification code via SMS. Please enter the received verification code and click on &quot;Complete Registration&quot;.</li>
<li>You are ready to start playing! Please enter your username and password to log into your account.</li>
</ol>
</div>